MAP_Dat_Producao:
mapping Load
	VBELN,
    date(ERDAT) as DAT_PRODUCAO
from [lib://CNNDIR-Dados/Extraídos/SAP ECC/LOG-LEADTIME/LIKP.qvd] (qvd)
